# autocrop

A CLI tool for automatically cropping videos.

## Installation

```bash
pip install autocrop-video
```

## Usage

```bash
autocrop process path/to/input_video.mp4
```

For more options, run:

```bash
autocrop --help
```

## Requirements

- Python 3.7+
- FFmpeg and FFprobe installed and accessible from the command line